Package: textpress
Type: Package
Title: A Lightweight and Versatile NLP Toolkit
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jason", "Timm", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "JaTimm@salud.unm.edu"))
Maintainer: Jason Timm <JaTimm@salud.unm.edu>
Description: A lightweight R toolkit for text retrieval. Four-stage pipeline: Fetch (URLs from search/Wikipedia), Read (content from URLs), Process (split, tokenize, index), Search (regex, BM25, vector similarity, dictionary). Verb_noun naming; minimal dependencies. Embeddings built elsewhere and passed in for semantic search.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    httr,
    Matrix,
    rvest,
    stringi, 
    stringr,
    xml2,
    pbapply,
    jsonlite,
    lubridate
Suggests:
    SnowballC (>= 0.7.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/jaytimm/textpress, https://jaytimm.github.io/textpress/
BugReports: https://github.com/jaytimm/textpress/issues
